modName: Real Estate - ALL cozy and lore friendly PLAYER HOMES from Nexus
summary: I made a list of all cozy/lore-friendly player houses/homes with screenshots (no god/cheat homes!), to buy or not and/or by pack or not with quests or not. Very usefull to choose \"quickly\". You can install all of them, just check that houses are not at the same place on the map of course...! 2 Buildable homes, 3 homes packs and + 60 homes.
descriptionHtml:
It was for myself first, to clarify my mind^^
I made a list of all cozy/lore-friendly player houses/homes with screenshots (no god/cheat homes!), to buy or not and/or by pack or not with quests or not. Very usefull to choose \"quickly\". You can install all homes,  just check that it aren\'t at the same place on the map! 2 buildable homes mods, 4 homes packs and + 60 homes.

=>DON\'T be afraid to go to the last number in the list, because some exterior houses are not really original, but interiors may be awesome (like number 67 ;) ), thus \"always\" click on \"download\". The choice never be so difficult...!
PS: Riverwood seems to be the place to be^^
